abindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gbi1665702728021.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gbi1665702728021.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gbi1665702728021.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gbi1665702728021\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Informix Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__informix_connector_options_151190\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To set connector options, use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</span> assignment setting in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__topic_d49760e1_d49761e1_d49762e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49763e1_d49764e1_d49765e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n\n         </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__topic_d32707e1_d32708e1_d32709e1_d32710e1_d32711e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d618705e74\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24176e1_d24177e1_d24178e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49769e1_d49770e1_d49771e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kor1665702728089.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kor1665702728089.html\" title=\"Specify when constraint checking should be performed.\">checking</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24179e1_d24180e1_d24181e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49772e1_d49773e1_d49774e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzr1665702728165.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzr1665702728165.html\" title=\"Set the connection mechanism to be used by the INF connector.\">connection</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24182e1_d24183e1_d24184e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49775e1_d49776e1_d49777e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxl1665702728234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxl1665702728234.html\" title=\"Allow Informix to manage referential integrity (instead of Uniface).\">dbms ri</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24185e1_d24186e1_d24187e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49778e1_d49779e1_d49780e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"goo1665702728302.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/goo1665702728302.html\" title=\"Delimit all database object names.\">delimident</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24188e1_d24189e1_d24190e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49781e1_d49782e1_d49783e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzb1665702728379.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzb1665702728379.html\" title=\"Specify the engine type that Informix uses.\">Engine Type</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ftl1727955765003.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ftl1727955765003.html\" title=\"Specify the maximum size of field names.\">field name size</a></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24191e1_d24192e1_d24193e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49784e1_d49785e1_d49786e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xdy1665702728451.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xdy1665702728451.html\" title=\"Create decimals with no scaling as fixed point decimal (p,0).\">fixed point</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24194e1_d24195e1_d24196e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49787e1_d49788e1_d49789e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mmd1665702728518.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mmd1665702728518.html\" title=\"Prevent cursors from being closed across database commits.\">hold cursors</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24197e1_d24198e1_d24199e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49790e1_d49791e1_d49792e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srb1665702728590.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srb1665702728590.html\" title=\"Set the isolation level at which the application will run.\">IsolationLevel</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24200e1_d24201e1_d24202e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49793e1_d49794e1_d49795e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pmd1665702561226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pmd1665702561226.html\" title=\"Set error to 100 when an error occurs on the read/lock.\">lock</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24203e1_d24204e1_d24205e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49796e1_d49797e1_d49798e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mya1665702728665.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mya1665702728665.html\" title=\"Control operations that access locked records.\">lockmode</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24206e1_d24207e1_d24208e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49799e1_d49800e1_d49801e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vda1665702728733.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vda1665702728733.html\" title=\"Enable multi-byte character sets.\">multi byte</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24209e1_d24210e1_d24211e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49802e1_d49803e1_d49804e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fag1665702938207.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fag1665702938207.html\" title=\"Create Nchar and Nvarchar fields (instead of Char and Varchar) at table creation.\">nls</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24212e1_d24213e1_d24214e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49805e1_d49806e1_d49807e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lbw1665702728801.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lbw1665702728801.html\" title=\"Enable stored procedures.\">procs</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24215e1_d24216e1_d24217e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49808e1_d49809e1_d49810e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vvq1665702552959.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvq1665702552959.html\" title=\"Set the access mode.\">read</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24218e1_d24219e1_d24220e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49811e1_d49812e1_d49813e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ynf1665702728873.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ynf1665702728873.html\" title=\"Declares a new cursor.\">rebuildcursor</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24221e1_d24222e1_d24223e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49814e1_d49815e1_d49816e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lqj1665702728942.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lqj1665702728942.html\" title=\"Insert specific values into serial fields.\">serial insert</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mzj1727955704907.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mzj1727955704907.html\" title=\"Sets the maximum size of table names in the database.\">table name size</a></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24224e1_d24225e1_d24226e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49817e1_d49818e1_d49819e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qbr1665702729010.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbr1665702729010.html\" title=\"Retrieve trimmed Char data from service stored procedures.\">trim</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24227e1_d24228e1_d24229e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49820e1_d49821e1_d49822e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tdr1665702729081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdr1665702729081.html\" title=\"Allow wildcard literals in actual data.\">wildcard literals</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__topic_d32712e1_d32713e1_d32714e1_d32715e1_d32716e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d618705e345\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49826e1_d49827e1_d49828e1\">Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non-negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__topic_d32717e1_d32718e1_d32719e1_d32720e1_d32721e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d618705e354\">\n                        \n Syntax Rules\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49832e1_d49833e1_d49834e1\">The syntax rules for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</span> are as follows:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24230e1_d24231e1_d24232e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49835e1_d49836e1_d49837e1\">The assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24233e1_d24234e1_d24235e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49838e1_d49839e1_d49840e1\">Each option may be specified once.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24236e1_d24237e1_d24238e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49841e1_d49842e1_d49843e1\">The order in which the options are specified is not significant.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24239e1_d24240e1_d24241e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49844e1_d49845e1_d49846e1\">Multiple options must be separated by a comma.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24242e1_d24243e1_d24244e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49847e1_d49848e1_d49849e1\">Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__li_d24245e1_d24246e1_d24247e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gbi1665702728021__p_d49850e1_d49851e1_d49852e1\">Options are not case-dependent.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$INF_PARAMS dbms ri, nls, procs, lockmode wait</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a><p>Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527781\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527781\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Informix Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Informix Connector Options To set connector options, use the USYS$INF_PARAMS assignment setting in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$INF_PARAMS Option { , Option n Options checking connection dbms ri delimident Engine Type field name size fixed point hold cursors IsolationLevel lock lockmode multi byte nls procs read rebuildcursor serial insert table name size trim wildcard literals Description Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non-negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific. Syntax Rules The syntax rules for USYS$INF_PARAMS are as follows: The assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file. Each option may be specified once. The order in which the options are specified is not significant. Multiple options must be separated by a comma. Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs. Options are not case-dependent. For example: USYS$INF_PARAMS dbms ri, nls, procs, lockmode wait Copy Related Links [DRIVER_SETTINGS] Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}